  "preFix": {
    "title": "Tapping for turning 40",
    "subtitle": "A tapping practice for the feelings that come with a decade change",
    "excerpt": "A tapping practice for the specific emotional weight that arrives with a significant birthday: the audit it triggers, the gap between where you are and where you expected to be, and the permission to begin again.",
    "sourceNotes": "EFT (Emotional Freedom Technique) developed by Gary Craig (1990s). Script and framing original to homemade.education.",
    "body": {
      "type": "doc",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "A five-minute tapping practice for the feelings a significant birthday brings up. The audit. The gap between where you are and where you expected to be. The script works with the comparison and the grief, and makes room for what the new decade might be.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "how EFT tapping works",
              "type": "text",
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "link",
                  "attrs": {
                    "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": " first.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "The practice",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Karate chop",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Even though this birthday is bringing up more than I expected, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Even though I compare myself to a version of this age I made up, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Even though turning 40 feels like a reckoning, I am open to it also being a beginning.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Tapping round",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Eyebrow:** I didn't expect to feel this way about a birthday.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Side of eye:** I'm comparing my real life to an imagined 40-year-old.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Under eye:** Some things I expected to have by now, I don't.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Under nose:** I'm not where I thought I'd be, and that's a grief.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Chin:** I also didn't expect to have the things I do have.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Collarbone:** The blueprint was drawn by someone who didn't know me yet.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Under arm:** 40 is allowed to be different from what I imagined.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Top of head:** The number is real. The blueprint was fiction.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Reframe to positive",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Eyebrow:** My 40s belong to me.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Side of eye:** I get to write this decade from the inside.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Under eye:** Some things I wanted are still ahead.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Under nose:** Some things I have now, I couldn't have imagined wanting.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Chin:** I am more myself at 40 than I was at 30.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Collarbone:** There is time.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Under arm:** This decade can be a beginning.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "**Top of head:** I am allowed to like being 40.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Tap each round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Where this practice comes from",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Gary Craig developed EFT in the 1990s. Script original to homemade.education.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
